    <a title="Shaun McCarthy" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/63832666-shaun-mccarthy"><img alt="Shaun McCarthy" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1484341749p2/63832666.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
