<span id="freeTextContainer1574578661163877888">The Trigger is a fascinating account of the lead up to WWI. <br/><br/>It reveals the complexities of the Balkans and the internecine strife between the various religious factions at that time, and sets the scene for the latter troubles in the Bosnian war in the 80&apos;s.<br/><br/>If you want an understanding of the region, this is a must read.</span>
  <span id="freeText1574578661163877888" style="display:none">The Trigger is a fascinating account of the lead up to WWI. <br /><br />It reveals the complexities of the Balkans and the internecine strife between the various religious factions at that time, and sets the scene for the latter troubles in the Bosnian war in the 80's.<br /><br />If you want an understanding of the region, this is a must read.</span>
